 final Olympic qualifier, with the second leg to come on Tuesday at Loftus Stadium.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999861302, \"rank\": 1.3977900487175669e-11, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only the winner over the two legs will advance to the Women's Olympic Football Tournament later this year.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999992010089, \"rank\": 7.990889154616679e-10, \"text\": \"Olympic Football Tournament\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is important to qualify for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the coming years I will not be here, so to play in one last Olympics will mean a lot for me,\\\" said the 38 year old Matlou from Abuja, where Banyana are preparing for the meeting with the Super Falcons.\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.06637627624161e-21, \"text\": \"Abuja\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matlou previously played for Banyana at the 2012 Olympic Games in London and the 2016 Olympics in Rio De Janeiro, while the side missed out on a place in Tokyo four years ago.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9997932345576122, \"rank\": 0.00012433154313751265, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1016, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.8757247824909711, \"rank\": 0.14191127166181114, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9968641677767514, \"rank\": 0.0031456603190726505, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a very important encounter against Nigeria \\u2026 we missed out in 2020 and this time we have to make sure we qualify,\\\" added Matlou, who is still playing her club football in Spain with Spanish club Eibar.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999861302, \"rank\": 1.3977900487175669e-11, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"w