team that goes to the Olympics,\\\" said Motau.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Especially for the locally-based players \\u2026 It is very important to be there, so that we can showcase our talent.\\\"\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are 17 locally-based players, indeed, in the Banyana squad, with just seven based overseas, including Matlou, captain Refiloe Jane and star striker Thembi Kgatlana.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1946, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refiloe_Jane\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Refiloe Jane\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refiloe_Jane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refiloe_Jane\"}, {\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thembi_Kgatlana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thembi Kgatlana\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thembi_Kgatlana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thembi_Kgatlana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Motau says that it is good for the locally-based players to learn from the overseas-based talent in the squad.\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is always good to have them in camp, they let us know what to expect,\\\" added Motau.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Super Falcons of Nigeria were finally able to welcome attacking superstar Asisat Oshoala into their camp as she arrived yesterday, along with\\u00a0Chinwendu Ihezuo and Esther Okoronkwo, to complete Nigeria's 22-woman squad.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2273, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asisat_Oshoala\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Asisat Oshoa